{"tid":1685082,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【反共心法】港女從今日起唔再叫港女","createTime":"2019-10-31T11:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T11:19:33.000Z","uid":259321,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1cd5c0e4e66aba2845be813a38e208273c78254","tid":1685082,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:18:43.000Z","msg":"香港開埠過百年<br />\n你估你老母祖老母當年唔蒲唔任性咩？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解係回歸之後</span></strong>香港女仔先開始被人叫港女先？<br />\n回歸之後將香港女仔<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">標籤為「港女」</span></strong><br />\n同區旗用左<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>絕子絕孫嘅洋紫荊</strong></span>做香港棵花一樣<br />\n係中共喺香港大玩嘅<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>邪惡心理學</strong></span>同[black]<strong>暗黑風水學</strong>[/black]<br />\n神龜入海，幾個飯剷頭，連成一綫劏開香港嘅回歸紀念塔，陰司紙設計嘅新紅衫魚數都數唔晒<br />\n所有嘢都係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>破壞香港風水</strong></span><br />\n (風水信不信由你，但對家就係咁嘅意圖)<br />\n要香港人絕子絕孫<br />\n令香港喺呢個優秀文明<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">從地球上消失</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日反共 (中共，港共，土共，暗共乜乜都好)<br />\n首先由<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">修正意識形態</span></strong>做起<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></div><br />\n宜家同我一人一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港女仔優點</strong></span>！！！<br />\n我先！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1）係講純正香港廣東話<br />\n2）<br />\n3）<br />\n</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n（唔好再話廣東話係你母語，冇人會係本地講自己語言係母語，目的係要令香港人對本土產生疏離感，一樣係邪惡心理學嚟。）</span>"},{"pid":"176e051822c01d0f939b341306cfa6672bcf82e7","tid":1685082,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/niD2F9u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FniD2F9u.jpg&h=2d7b5e0f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}